    "source_text": "我們瞭解我們在這重要領域仍然任重道遠。我們最近亦完成環境、社會及管治策略的檢討。本人充滿信心，我們\n的五大策略焦點領域：提升身心健康、綠色營運、可持續投資、人才與文化和有效的管治，將有助我們實現在環",
    "current_translation": "We understand that we still have a long way to go in this important area. We have also recently completed a review of our Environmental, Social and Governance strategy. I am confident that our five strategic focus areas—enhancing physical and mental wellbeing, green operations, sustainable investment, talent and culture, and effective governance—will help us achieve our aspiration to be a leader globally in Environmental, Social and Governance."
  },
